First do a Getting Started task.

This task consists of modifying testsuites/sptests/sp09 per the instructions at http://www.rtems.org/wiki/index.php/GoogleCodeInProjects#sp09_Refactoring. You will need to create a new test (sptimer_err01 and sptimer_err02) based on 01 for non-server cases and 02 for server cases from screen 14.
A patch generated using git diff will need to be submitted to fulfill this task. This patch will be reviewed by the mentors and suggestions are likely to be made.
